      <h1>Confirmation Statement: deadlines, what to file, and what changes need declaring</h1>
      <p class="canonical"><strong>Question:</strong> What is a confirmation statement and how do I file it?</p>
      <p class="excerpt"><strong>Excerpt:</strong> A confirmation statement is a mandatory annual filing with Companies House that verifies your company's key information, ensuring public records are accurate and up-to-date.</p>
      <table class="meta">
