      <h1>Dealing with HMRC VAT letters and queries</h1>
      <p class="canonical"><strong>Question:</strong> How do I understand and respond to HMRC VAT letters and queries?</p>
      <p class="excerpt"><strong>Excerpt:</strong> tool_code print(google_search.search(queries=[&quot;HMRC VAT letters common reasons&quot;, &quot;how to respond to HMRC VAT query&quot;, &quot;HMRC VAT penalty letter explanation&quot;, &quot;VAT deferred adjustment meaning HMRC&quot;, &quot;changing VAT number…</p>
