      <h1>What VAT you can reclaim on business expenses</h1>
      <p class="canonical"><strong>Question:</strong> What VAT can I reclaim on business expenses and what are the correct rates?</p>
      <p class="excerpt"><strong>Excerpt:</strong> Navigating VAT reclamation can significantly impact your business's cash flow, allowing you to recover Value Added Tax (VAT) paid on eligible business expenses.</p>
